    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hello! If this is you are trying to achieve you can do it by this method. \r\n\r\n\r\nconst [showMoreTriggered, setShowMoreTriggered] = React.useState<boolean>(false)\r\n\r\n<RefinementList\r\n                  attribute=\"brand\"\r\n                  sortBy={[sorting]}\r\n                  limit={showMoreTriggered ? 20 : 5}\r\n                  showMore={true}\r\n                  showMoreLimit={21}\r\n                  onClick = {() => setShowMoreTriggered(!showMoreTriggered)}\r\n                />\r\n\r\n",
